snippet.textDisplay:
I absolutely loved this. We adore every single one of them.
I do want to say this, I'm sure she's just lovely, but Marta Kaufman needs to perhaps live in the moment. She had these legends of comedy and Hollywood all in one place. However, she kept stepping all over the chemistry that this cast has. Lily Tomlin had us in stitches but Marta couldn't seem to let those moments have any life. It's unlikely that we'll get all these great people on a series together again and we should just sit back and enjoy their antics.
I'm not trying to be rude or unfriendly. I was just making an observation. This show brings our home so much joy.

snippet.textDisplay: Big shout out and thank you to Netflix is a joke and the cast and crew of grace and Frankie. Thank you guys so much for doing that for all of us grace and Frankie fans. It was great for me to see all of you in a different light, so to speak. You gave me a lot of laughs tonight and I thank you all for that. I’m glad this was for meals on wheels. My mother is 93 and I visit her weekly. I go to her apartment building and we meet outside and sit 12 feet apart. I saw people in her building all the time during normal times who use and need meals on wheels. This is so important for our seniors.
